The first read already shows a useful shape: the bridge no longer imports `compat/index.js` directly. Its “native” path is actually an MCP stdio subprocess through `bin/mk-skill-advisor-launcher.cjs`, and any probe exception is swallowed before it falls back to the legacy `route:"python"` envelope.
