ket","direct launcher invocation printed LEASE_HELD_BY:26585 ... (no-bridge-socket)"]},{"id":"F4-004","severity":"important","label":"compat entrypoint is healthy and should be the bridge primary path","evidence":[".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/compat/index.ts:5 exports handleAdvisorRecommend",".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/compat/index.ts:6 exports readAdvisorStatus",".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/compat/index.ts:7 exports probeAdvisorDaemon",".opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/dist/mcp_server/compat/index.js:4 mirrors handleAdvisorRecommend export","direct import listed buildSkillAdvisorBrief, handleAdvisorRecommend, probeAdvisorDaemon, readAdvisorStatus, renderAdvisorBrief","direct readAdvisorStatus returned freshness live generation 4466 skillCount 23"]}],"remediation":["Update .opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/mcp_server/plugin_bridges/mk-skill-advisor-bridge.mjs so loadNativeAdvisorModules imports ../dist/mcp_server/compat/index.js first and only falls back to launcher MCP subprocess on import failure.","Update .opencode/bin/lib/launcher-ipc-bridge.cjs or .opencode/bin/mk-skill-advisor-launcher.cjs so held lease without daemon-ipc.sock is stale/reclaimable or machine-readable failure, not non-JSON stdout in an MCP client path."],"nextFocus":"F5 stale vitest path NC-004/005"}
